A vintage 1950s-style illustration of a mechanical assembly line where glowing spreadsheet grids flow through ornate brass gears and clockwork mechanisms, transforming into neat stacks of index cards emerging on the other side. The scene features warm sepia and copper tones with touches of sage green, showing intricate Victorian-era industrial machinery with pipes and valves. Steam wisps curl around the apparatus as data cells visually morph mid-journey through the contraption. The perspective is slightly isometric, showcasing the full transformation pipeline from chaotic grid to organized archive.
